          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
            <span class="text-[#FF4B4B] text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">#2 Best Seller</span>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mt-1">모노크롬 스니커즈</h3>
