          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden reveal" style="--delay: 2;">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594938298603-c8148c4dae35?q=80&w=800" alt="베스트 3" class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
            <span class="text-[#FF4B4B] text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">#3 Best Seller</span>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mt-1">미니멀 크로스백</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm font-outfit mt-1">198,000원</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== Brand Story ========== -->
  <section id="story" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-8 reveal" style="--delay: 0;">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-[#FF4B4B]">Brand Story</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter font-outfit">
          본질에 집중하는<br>브랜드 철학
